{
  "text": "\u2022 the fact that the coefficients of the polynomial in the Chebyshev basis of polynomials can be computed very efficiently using the Fast Fourier Transform (FFT) algorithm of [CITATION_1] , which has a complexity of O(K log K) for the computation of K coefficients.",
